          "description": "Limits the number of the rows that are computed in the query that is the source of the data used for this chart.",
          "data_type": "integer",
          "enum_values": [
            10,
            50,
            100,
            250,
            500,
            1000,
            5000,
            10000,
            50000
          ],
          "sample_data": 10000,
          "required": false,
          "embedding": "否",
          "default_value": 10000
        },
        {
          "field_name": "sort_by_metric",
          "description": "Whether to sort results by the selected metric in descending order.",
          "data_type": "boolean",
          "enum_values": [
            true,
            false
          ],
          "sample_data": false,
          "required": false,
          "embedding": "否",
          "default_value": null,
          "ui_default_state": "unchecked",
          "notes": "shared control 没有显式 `default`；`getControlState.ts` 只有在 `state.default` 为 truthy 时才会把默认值写入 control.value，因此 untouched root form_data 的缺省态通常是未设置。与此同时，`CheckboxControl.jsx` 的 `defaultProps.value=false` 且 `checked={!!value}`，所以 UI 会以未勾选状态展示。只有为 true 时，`buildQuery.ts` 才会追加 `orderby=[[metric, false]]`。"
        }
      ],
      "Chart Options": [
